\subtree{
\title{Key Insight}
\blockquote{\strong{The oracle is the market.}}

\p{Since \code{\startverb color_at(seed, index)\stopverb} is deterministic and unforgeable, the prediction market has \em{perfect settlement}. No disputes possible—the color either matches or it doesn't.}

\p{This is "multiversal" because different seeds explore different derivation paths through the same generative function. Betting = choosing which multiverse to observe.}
}
}